      <title>博尔索纳罗告诉巴西最高法院，他没有向匈牙利寻求庇护</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/bolsonaro-tells-brazil-s-top-court-he-didn-t-seek-asylum-with-hungary</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西前总统雅伊尔·博尔索纳罗的辩护律师告诉最高法院，在没有充分理由让他在祖国被捕的情况下，怀疑他向匈牙利寻求政治庇护是“不合逻辑的”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/bolsonaro-tells-brazil-s-top-court-he-didn-t-seek-asylum-with-hungary</guid>
