    <item>
      <title>在米雷紧缩政策之前，阿根廷的贫困率已接近流行病水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/argentine-poverty-neared-pandemic-levels-before-milei-austerity</link>
      <description><![CDATA[甚至在总统哈维尔·米莱的休克疗法生效之前，阿根廷的贫困水平在 2023 年下半年就略有上升，因为通货膨胀飙升，打击了家庭消费能力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/argentine-poverty-neared-pandemic-levels-before-milei-austerity</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 19:21:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>耶伦警告中国工业增长正在扭曲世界经济</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/yellen-sounds-alarm-on-china-roiling-world-with-industry-ramp-up</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国财政部长珍妮特·耶伦(Janet Yellen)抨击中国利用补贴为关键新兴行业的制造商提供竞争优势，但代价是扭曲全球经济，并表示她计划在即将到来的访问中就这一问题向中国施压。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/yellen-sounds-alarm-on-china-roiling-world-with-industry-ramp-up</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 11:49:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
